6	/**
7	 * Serve a project's built page bundle at `/app/<project>/*` (Phase 5B).
8	 *
9	 * The integrator registers this handler AFTER the app-api route (Phase 3), so
10	 * `…/app/<project>/api/*` is already consumed and never reaches here — every
11	 * request we see is a page/asset request for the SPA.
12	 *
13	 * ── Serving model ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
14	 * The build (Phase 5A `buildProjectPages`) hands us an `outDir` (…/.data/pages-dist)
15	 * plus an `assetManifest: string[]` — the exact set of real files it emitted. We
16	 * serve on a manifest-match basis:
17	 *   • sub-path IS in the manifest → serve that static file from `outDir`
18	 *   • sub-path is NOT in the manifest → serve `outDir/index.html` (SPA fallback)
